top_actions.description: Identify and fix technical issues such as errors, difficulties with certain features, and problems with the app's functionality to ensure a smooth user experience.

top_actions.description: Simplify and streamline the withdrawal process to reduce difficulties and high charges, ensuring that users can easily withdraw their money when needed.
